16:00:03.03 -- workaround missing pcall in zfs lua implementation
16:00:03.03 local function tuple(...)
16:00:03.03   return {n=select('#', ...), ...}
16:00:03.03 end
16:00:03.03 
16:00:03.03 function pcall(f, ...)
16:00:03.03   local co = coroutine.create(f)
16:00:03.03   local res = tuple(coroutine.resume(co, ...))
16:00:03.03   if res[1] and coroutine.status(co) == "suspended" then
16:00:03.03     res[1] = false
16:00:03.03   end
16:00:03.03   return table.unpack(res, 1, res.n)
16:00:03.03 end

16:00:03.03 -- workaround missing math lib in zfs lua implementation
16:00:03.03 local A1, A2 = 727595, 798405  -- 5^17=D20*A1+A2
16:00:03.03 local D20, D40 = 1048576, 1099511627776  -- 2^20, 2^40
16:00:03.03 local X1, X2 = 0, 1
16:00:03.03 function rand()
16:00:03.03     local U = X2*A2
16:00:03.03     local V = (X1*A2 + X2*A1) % D20
16:00:03.03     V = (V*D20 + U) % D40
16:00:03.03     X1 = V/D20
16:00:03.03     X2 = V - X1*D20
16:00:03.03     return V*100/D40
16:00:03.03 end

16:00:03.03 local function check (t)
16:00:03.03   local function f(a, b) assert(a and b); return true end
16:00:03.03   local s, e = pcall(table.sort, t, f)
16:00:03.03   assert(not s and e:find("invalid order function"))
16:00:03.03 end

16:00:03.03 function check (a, f)
16:00:03.03   f = f or function (x,y) return x<y end;
16:00:03.03   for n = #a, 2, -1 do
16:00:03.03     assert(not f(a[n], a[n-1]))
16:00:03.03   end
16:00:03.03 end

16:00:03.03 function perm (s, n)
16:00:03.03   n = n or #s
16:00:03.03   if n == 1 then
16:00:03.03     local t = {unpack(s)}
16:00:03.03     table.sort(t)
16:00:03.03     check(t)
16:00:03.03   else
16:00:03.03     for i = 1, n do
16:00:03.03       s[i], s[n] = s[n], s[i]
16:00:03.03       perm(s, n - 1)
16:00:03.03       s[i], s[n] = s[n], s[i]
16:00:03.03     end
16:00:03.03   end

16:00:03.08 -- workaround missing pcall in zfs lua implementation
16:00:03.08 local function tuple(...)
16:00:03.08   return {n=select('#', ...), ...}
16:00:03.08 end
16:00:03.08 
16:00:03.08 function pcall(f, ...)
16:00:03.08   local co = coroutine.create(f)
16:00:03.08   local res = tuple(coroutine.resume(co, ...))
16:00:03.08   if res[1] and coroutine.status(co) == "suspended" then
16:00:03.08     res[1] = false
16:00:03.08   end
16:00:03.08   return table.unpack(res, 1, res.n)
16:00:03.08 end

16:00:03.08 -- workaround missing math lib in zfs lua implementation
16:00:03.08 local A1, A2 = 727595, 798405  -- 5^17=D20*A1+A2
16:00:03.08 local D20, D40 = 1048576, 1099511627776  -- 2^20, 2^40
16:00:03.08 local X1, X2 = 0, 1
16:00:03.08 function rand()
16:00:03.08     local U = X2*A2
16:00:03.08     local V = (X1*A2 + X2*A1) % D20
16:00:03.08     V = (V*D20 + U) % D40
16:00:03.08     X1 = V/D20
16:00:03.08     X2 = V - X1*D20
16:00:03.08     return V*100/D40
16:00:03.08 end
